('fd638584-6587-5539-bbf5-c8caeee512ff', 'e9bc7f35-71ca-4333-a4cc-60b0f97f5046', 'The patient complained of sharp pain in his ___ after eating something unusual.', '病人在吃了一些不尋常的東西後，抱怨其 ___ 有劇烈的疼痛。', 'abdomen', 'ankle', 'elbow', 'forehead', 'abdomen 指的是身體的腹部區域。', '想像壞男人 (a bad men) 踢了你的 abdomen (腹部)。', '2026-07-06 15:53:38', '2026-07-06 15:53:38'),
('a8554d9a-874a-5c01-a406-a21eb0f3353b', '3b226ad5-3dff-42de-aba3-a1566022a5de', 'Many ___ people face various emotional challenges as they transition from childhood to adulthood.', '許多青少年在從童年過渡到成年階段時，會面臨各種情緒上的挑戰。', 'adolescent', 'elderly', 'professional', 'ancient', 'ad (朝向) + olesce (成長/變大) → 指正在成長、邁向成年的階段。', 'ad (去) + olesce (成長) → 正在長大的 → 青少年。', '2026-07-06 17:57:21', '2026-07-06 17:57:21'),
('c552a54e-933d-5d42-9062-aaa83c9429d3', '2c102275-ed9b-4b5c-837e-febb37aa5d3c', 'The local residents are strongly ___ the proposal to build a new factory in the area.', '當地居民強烈反對在該地區建造新工廠的提案。', 'against', 'during', 'beside', 'toward', 'against 為介系詞，在此句中表示「反對」某種立場或計畫。', '記住 against 代表「對立」或「對抗」，就像在比賽中與對手對抗一樣。', '2026-07-06 18:51:56', '2026-07-06 18:51:56'),
('b4a68ad8-7725-56ea-8712-013e3df7d5bf', '3034e414-9217-4e33-9008-91d537d6c01e', 'She has ___ evidence to support her theory, making her argument very convincing.', '她有充裕的證據來支持她的理論，使她的論點非常有說服力。', 'ample', 'scarce', 'vague', 'trivial', '源自拉丁語 amplus，意為「寬大的」或「廣闊的」。', '聯想發音「安普」→「安普提供充裕的資源」，幫助記憶其「充裕的」之意。', '2026-07-06 20:53:13', '2026-07-06 20:53:13'),
('9228877d-a796-56ae-990a-1a8e8ac210cf', '0582c060-dd58-400e-aeb5-8689ab936248', 'I''m still hungry. I want ___ apple.', '我還餓，我想再吃一個蘋果。', 'another', 'many', 'several', 'all', 'an (一個) + other (其他的) → 另一個', 'an (一個) + other (其他的) = 另一個', '2026-07-06 14:18:20', '2026-07-06 14:18:20'),
('a3687de8-06e2-5b72-a4ca-980ef9f39933', '1e07a688-c1ea-41cb-8a4e-84690cec243c', 'The committee will meet tomorrow to ___ the new proposal, which has received overwhelming support from the members.', '委員會將於明天開會以批准這個已獲得成員壓倒性支持的新提案。', 'approve', 'reject', 'predict', 'prepare', 'ad- (趨向) + prove (證明) → 證明某事是正確的 → 批准、贊成', '想像你在向 (ad-) 別人證明 (prove) 這個計畫是沒問題的 → 批准', '2026-07-06 23:23:31', '2026-07-06 23:23:31'),
('3e7b65fd-5349-5fc2-ad76-3bab22924627', '863f960c-9dea-4632-a9cb-3487b5c50eab', 'The birds ___ in the trees.', '那些鳥在樹上。', 'are', 'run', 'jump', 'sing', 'be 動詞，用於複數主詞表示「在某處」。', '複數主詞 (The birds) → are', '2026-07-05 11:32:46', '2026-07-05 11:32:46'),
