('cb613acb-e5c1-5994-b26c-510fa515dc0b', 'd667c061-2c22-45e8-9076-8f9dc69d5155', 'He wants to ___ a pilot in the future.', '他未來想要成為一名飛行員。', 'become', 'feel', 'look', 'stay', 'be (在/是) + come (來) → 來到某種狀態 → 變成', '走到 (come) 到某個狀態 (be) → 變成', '2026-07-07 02:56:59', '2026-07-07 02:56:59'),
('3d5eb3a3-d616-5900-9892-f8ce75c51dcf', 'dcf4a1e3-9671-42aa-ad21-716dd42330df', 'Please put the soup in a large ___ so it does not spill.', '請把湯裝在大碗裡，以免溢出來。', 'bowl', 'plate', 'cup', 'box', '名詞，指圓形且凹陷的容器。', 'bowl 的字形圓圓的，就像一個碗。', '2026-07-07 05:52:39', '2026-07-07 05:52:39'),
